Oct 12 -24

this model is based on the model:  
mCP-ngf-eIS2011FIGX1-mC170998D-I3-cl0/id-0/

with adjusted current amplitude in protocols adjusted from the IV curve of fig 4
(rather than from the example traces)
from:
[-185, -99, 157, 185, 341] 
to
[-161, -82, 139, 167, 293]

Features are also update:
* steady_state_voltage set to -83 for all protocols
* voltage_after_stim: removed
* maximum_voltage (stim 3): 53 to 51 
* steady_state_stimend (stim 3): 53 to 51
* minimum_votage (stim 1 and 2): removed
* sag_amplitude (stim 2): removed

* peak_voltage (stim 4 and 5): 22 to 20 +/- 1 to 3
* AHP_depth_abs std (stim 4 and 5) from 1 to 3

Simulation time increased in order to reduce depolarization block (frequent in older models)

